name: Coldplay Infinity tickets
summary: Coldplay has faced mixed reactions in their ticket sales for their upcoming UK and India tours. Some fans have expressed frustration with the "s**tshow" experience of trying to purchase tickets through Ticketmaster, complaining of being sent to the back of the queue and missing out on opportunities to attend shows. Conversely, others have been pleased with the release of "Infinity Tickets," a program offering affordable access to Coldplay concerts at a price point of $20. These tickets have been met with high demand and have sold out quickly. Despite the contrasting experiences, Coldplay is committed to providing fans with multiple chances to secure tickets through additional sales, providing hope for those who missed out in previous attempts.

According to reports, masked raiders armed with a machete forced their way into her £1 million Sunderland home. Crosby was upstairs with her two-year-old daughter at the time of the incident. Her fiancé, Jake Ankers, has spoken out about the ordeal, expressing his gratitude that Crosby and their child remained unharmed. The robbers reportedly left the scene before police arrived, and an investigation is underway.
